Rot et, here be three caerds or noates, or what the devil they be, left after all. Dang et, I have delivered ſeventeen—all the way from Mancheſter-ſquare to Petty France; from there to Biſhopſgate-ſtreet after ſweetmeats for Miſs, and then to the Hay-market about the pianny forty. Hang me if I doant make dead men of theſe
(tearing the notes);
dead men tell no tales. The people they were for, will never know their loſs. I can ſay I found nobody at hoam; ha, ha, ha! that was amoaſt the firſt word I larn'd, when I come to Lunnun—"Not at hoam, Sir." Dad! the gentry here have the cheapeſt way of entertaining their friends; it doesn't coſt above a dozen or two lies a day to keep acquaintance with great quality. Hey! did you ſpeak to me, Sir?

